gujarati.context:
Here is the translation:

This was done by Vitya Dan Char, it came to stand on life support; 
Her brother's name is Kesary, she came under Ghanshyam's shelter.

Here is the translation:

They have come on the earth, saying "you are my face", then they joined hands and said "servant"; 
The reason for coming today will be spoken, just as the Lord has decreed, so too it will happen.

Here is the translation:

Tell it to him that you have gone, your word will not be broken by you; 
Say this to Maharaja, a wonderful thing has been done so much in this matter.

Here is the translation:

He who has realized himself, knows his own worth; 
Don't consider a fool as ignorant; 
This is what men and women say, when they have found their master's burden heavy.

Here is the translation:

The story of Surat city, listen to it attentively I; 
Many Harijans live there, do worship of Swamishri's bhajan.

Here is the translation:

I trust that person as I trust God; 
But there's a new thing, listen to me, people of all directions.

Here is the translation:

"Lidho lochan bhari ne lao, jaanyu aavo naave fari dao;
Tiyaan naath rhyaa nav dan, didha baahu jivanu darshan."
